<section id="faq" class="section">
  <div class="faq-head reveal">
    <div class="eyebrow-mono" style="justify-content:center">Questions</div>
    <h2 class="sec-title">Questions, answered</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="faq-list reveal reveal-d1">
    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>Can I keep using Personal for free?<svg class="faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></summary>
      <div class="faq-answer"><p>Yes, forever. Personal gives you unlimited agents and every feature for a single player, with no credit card and no time limit.</p></div>
    </details>
    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>Who pays for a team?<svg class="faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></summary>
      <div class="faq-answer"><p>The team owner. Everyone you invite rides on the owner's plan, so members never enter a card of their own.</p></div>
    </details>
    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>What counts as a seat?<svg class="faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></summary>
      <div class="faq-answer"><p>One seat is one member who accepts your invite. Pending invites are free, and seats are prorated when people join or leave.</p></div>
    </details>
    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>What happens when my trial ends?<svg class="faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></summary>
      <div class="faq-answer"><p>Nothing is deleted. Your Space drops back to the free Personal plan and every agent and mission stays put. Add a card whenever you are ready to continue as a team.</p></div>
    </details>
    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>How do I move an agent into a team?<svg class="faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></summary>
      <div class="faq-answer"><p>Open the agent and share it with your Space. It keeps its history and skills, and your teammates can pick up any mission from where it stands.</p></div>
    </details>
    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>Do members need to pay or download anything?<svg class="faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></summary>
      <div class="faq-answer"><p>Members just accept the invite and download the free app. Billing stays with the owner.</p></div>
    </details>
  </div>
</section>
